x 0;">And Qualcomm is effectively backstopping SSW=E2=80=99s financing: Qua=
lcomm is on the hook to buy all of Veoneer if SSW doesn=E2=80=99t show up w=
ith financing.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a lot of ad hoc cap=
ital out there these days. The traditional way to take a company public is =
that you go to an investment bank, the investment bank sells your shares to=
 the public, the price you get depends on what the public market will pay, =
and the bank gets a cash fee when it finishes. The 2021 way to take a compa=
ny public is with a SPAC, a special purpose acquisition company: A sponsor =
