ated-in-advance=C2=A0price using the money in the investing pool, and is re=
warded with a chunk of the company and potentially huge upside.[3] Instead =
of going to a bank acting as agent, you go to a SPAC sponsor acting as prin=
cipal, backed by a pool of capital.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The tra=
